Interface BasicFeatureExtraction.OutcomeListener

  • Enclosing class:
    BasicFeatureExtraction

    public static interface BasicFeatureExtraction.OutcomeListener
    Allows user-defined behaviour upon success or failure of a transform job.

    Called when a feature extraction/transformation job completes.
